ent. Birds and bats may even suppress tropical arthropod outbreaks, although positive effects on plant growth are not always reported. As both bats and birds are major agents of pest suppression, a better understanding of the local and landscape factors driving the variability of their impact is needed.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Maas, Bea", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Karp, Daniel S.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Bumrungsri, Sara", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Darras, Kevin", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Gonthier, David", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Huang, Joe C.\u2010C.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Lindell, Catherine A.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Maine, Josiah J.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Mestre, Laia", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Michel, Nicole L.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Morrison, Emily B.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Perfecto, Ivette", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Philpott, Stacy M.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "\u015eekercio\u011flu, \u00c7agan H.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Silva, Roberta M.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Taylor, Peter J.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Tscharntke, Teja", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Van Bael, Sunshine A.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Whelan, Christopher J.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Williams\u2010Guill\u00e9n, Kimberly", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/4e4dcdfde050d2ce25c526da814dbcc4", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/389c919f1ca62fb77dd8a1c806e4ff4a1e662656f5a29c1175cd27296931981d", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/VS58K4P8", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/VS58K4P8", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "sche